---

<section
    class="section-tactics relative py-32 md:py-52 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-visible bg-transparent"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[-1] bg-[#121212]"></div>

        <div
            class="absolute top-[-15%] left-[-20%] w-[90%] h-[100%] bg-[#454E59]/60 blur-[160px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute bottom-[-15%] right-[-20%] w-[80%] h-[90%] bg-[#F2A663]/30 blur-[140px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#0D0D0D] via-transparent to-[#454E59]/25 opacity-100"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[1800px] mx-auto relative z-20 flex flex-col gap-24">
        <div
            class="w-full text-center space-y-8 translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
        >
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <span
                    class="text-[#A0A698] text-[10px] font-cinzel font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em]"
                    >Estrategia y Armonía</span
                >
                <div class="h-[1px] w-24 bg-[#A0A698]/50"></div>
            </div>

            <h2
                class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-9xl font-cinzel font-bold leading-[0.8] text-[#F2E6D8] tracking-tighter"
            >
                Dominio <br />
                <span
                    class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#A0A698] via-[#F2A663] to-[#BF7E7E]"
                >
                    Total
                </span>
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start"
        >
            <div
                class="flex flex-col gap-10 items-center text-center relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-20 bg-[#F2A663]/15 blur-[100px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="relative w-full p-2 border-2 border-double border-[#454E59]/60 bg-[#0D0D0D]/70 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-700 group-hover:border-[#F2A663]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute -top-1 -left-1 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#F2A663]"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#F2A663]"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                        <img
                            src="/GreedFall/GreedFall_TheDyingWorld_Screenshot09.png"
                            alt="Combate con pausa táctica"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-[4000ms] group-hover:scale-105 opacity-90"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p
                    class="font-serif italic text-sm md:text-2xl text-[#F2E6D8]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-lg px-4"
                >
                    Enfréntate a tus enemigos y controla a tus compañeros en <span
                        class="text-[#F2A663] not-italic font-cinzel font-bold"
                        >combates dinámicos</span
                    > con pausa táctica.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col gap-10 items-center text-center relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-20 bg-[#BF7E7E]/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="relative w-full p-2 border-2 border-double border-[#BF7E7E]/60 bg-[#0D0D0D]/70 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-700 group-hover:border-[#F2E6D8]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#F2E6D8]"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-1 -left-1 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#F2E6D8]"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                        <img
                            src="/GreedFall/Screen_5.png"
                            alt="Olivier Derivière OST"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale transition-all duration-1000 group-hover:grayscale-0 opacity-80"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p
                    class="font-serif italic text-sm md:text-2xl text-[#F2E6D8]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-lg px-4"
                >
                    Una banda sonora original compuesta por <span
                        class="text-[#F2E6D8] not-italic font-cinzel font-bold underline decoration-[#BF7E7E]/40 underline-offset-8"
                        >Olivier Derivière</span
                    >, compositor de renombre.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-tactics {
        contain: paint;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(
            to bottom,
            transparent,
            black 15%,
            black 85%,
            transparent
        );
    }
</style>
